      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JANE'S JET (8) boasts a consistent overall record including 10 wins from 29 starts, the latest hitting the minor money when second (19.64) over 366m at Capalaba. Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Drawn out but with clear running expected to go close. MY ERNIE JAY (3) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by 4 lengths at this track in a handy 21.85 beating Weblec Jewel. Fair draw can see a good run and has a good record over this journey. Boasts four wins from four starts out of this box. Should feature again. GRANDIOSE GIRL (1) wasn't far away at the finish when 4th and beaten only 5 lengths (20.14) at this track. The form out of her last race has been franked. One of the main contenders. ROLLING ROYALTY (2) cannot be ruled out.",
